\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf3 \strokec3 The police don't have valid reasons to arrest people. This arrest is problematic for a number of reasons, but it does make it more possible for other Black folks to be arrested under similar circumstances.\'a0\cf2 \strokec2 \
